Mr. Patmore has been
experiencing pain every day

88
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:19,925
- for seven years.
- A cingulotomy could cause

89
00:04:20,027 --> 00:04:23,495
seizures, cognitive defects
or behavioral changes.

90
00:04:23,597 --> 00:04:27,031
