on my wife with my best friend.

137
00:06:56,132 --> 00:06:58,967
Everything's just
as it should be.

138
00:07:11,264 --> 00:07:14,415
Oh!

139
00:07:15,351 --> 00:07:18,102
Damn chair. Hang on.

140
