My toaster broke last month.

143
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:26,678
Then my cat ran away and
my back porch collapsed.

144
00:07:26,780 --> 00:07:29,197
Also, my TV only
shows the color green.

145
00:07:29,299 --> 00:07:30,865
I'll get another chair.

146
00:07:32,769 --> 00:07:35,870
Don't bother. I'll
walk. Probably safer.

147
00:07:35,972 --> 00:07:38,673
No. Mr. O'Brien, you
need to stay in the chair.

148
00:07:38,775 --> 00:07:41,326
- It's hospital policy.
- I had three car accidents...

149
00:07:41,428 --> 00:07:46,280
Mr. O'Brien.

150
00:07:46,382 --> 00:07:48,399
Somebody get me
a gurney over here!

151
00:07:54,541 --> 00:07:58,042
- Sir, I am very sorry.
