152
00:07:58,145 --> 00:08:00,077
I am very, very sorry.

153
00:08:00,180 --> 00:08:02,947
Get him a CT. I want hourly
updates on his condition.

154
00:08:03,049 --> 00:08:05,450
- Yes, sir.
- You're gonna be OK.

155
