the beginning. I told him.

170
00:09:14,688 --> 00:09:16,053
He's Mark Sloan.

171
00:09:16,155 --> 00:09:18,289
You don't have a person
you talk to about things?

172
00:09:18,391 --> 00:09:21,075
You are the person
I talk to about things.

173
00:09:21,177 --> 00:09:23,356
I like to keep my
private life private

174
00:09:23,380 --> 00:09:26,514
from everyone, but most
definitely from Mark...

175
00:09:27,950 --> 00:09:29,801
Sloan.

176
00:09:38,277 --> 00:09:41,746
- How long'll the operation be?
- At least a couple of hours.

177
00:09:41,848 --> 00:09:43,247
Think it could be longer?

178
00:09:43,349 --> 00:09:46,451
If there are complications or
the mets are more extensive.

179
00:09:46,553 --> 00:09:47,797
They won't be, Jen.

180
00:09:47,821 --> 00:09:51,188
Please, stop. Call Mom
and Dad, tell them two hours.

181
