So I know I don't
know you, but spill.

184
00:10:08,525 --> 00:10:10,441
- Spill what?
- Anything.

185
00:10:10,543 --> 00:10:12,911
I'm begging you,
before she comes back

186
00:10:13,013 --> 00:10:15,457
and asks you to describe
my liver cell by cell.

187
00:10:15,481 --> 00:10:17,098
Please.

188
00:10:18,551 --> 00:10:22,153
OK. Um... Do you
want to hear about my

189
00:10:22,255 --> 00:10:23,921
stupid boss or stupid boyfriend?

190
00:10:24,024 --> 00:10:28,526
Oh! Boyfriend!
Definitely the boyfriend.

191
