199
00:10:59,793 --> 00:11:02,510
- I'm not being unreasonable.
- Pulse is coming down.

200
00:11:02,612 --> 00:11:06,547
But you have to admit,
you'd want them out.

201
00:11:06,649 --> 00:11:08,883
If you were me, you
would want them out.

202
00:11:12,889 --> 00:11:14,588
If we have to operate,

203
00:11:14,690 --> 00:11:17,358
I'll let you drill the
burr holes by yourself.

204
00:11:20,397 --> 00:11:23,131
Fine. I'd want
them out. Whatever.

205
00:11:23,233 --> 00:11:25,900
I knew it. OK, Mr. Patmore.

206
00:11:26,002 --> 00:11:29,487
OK, we're gonna
change your position.

207
00:11:31,007 --> 00:11:34,242
- I think I have an idea...
- No, don't think. Know.

208
00:11:34,344 --> 00:11:36,644
Run to the lab
for his test results.

