221
00:12:17,970 --> 00:12:19,570
Pathetic.

222
00:12:20,673 --> 00:12:23,040
Yes. I know, I'm pathetic.

223
00:12:23,142 --> 00:12:26,227
I did read this article. I do
have a photographic memory.

224
00:12:26,329 --> 00:12:29,063
Chief's on his new thing
with the interns to be heard...

225
00:12:29,165 --> 00:12:32,784
- Use fewer words, Grey.
- I think he needs an ENT.

226
00:12:33,854 --> 00:12:36,037
You're an ENT, right?

227
00:12:36,139 --> 00:12:39,440
How are you doing
in there, Mr. O'Brien?

228
00:12:39,542 --> 00:12:43,527
