couple more minutes. Hang on.

230
00:12:48,484 --> 00:12:51,352
Guess what I
found. An apartment.

231
00:12:51,454 --> 00:12:53,370
A beautiful apartment.

232
00:12:53,456 --> 00:12:56,174
