honest-to-God fires in...

234
00:12:58,745 --> 00:13:01,012
and I can't afford it by myself.

235
00:13:01,114 --> 00:13:04,231
So... I thought if you
could get over yourself

236
00:13:04,333 --> 00:13:06,417
we could live together.

237
00:13:08,254 --> 00:13:09,887
No, thanks.

238
00:13:11,257 --> 00:13:14,391
I mention the hardwood floors,
the honest-to-God fireplace?

239
